title: Swig Waiting for World to Reopen
itunes:title: Swig Waiting for World to Reopen
description:
Kent Swig, President at Swig Equities, discusses the impact the coronavirus outbreak is having on residential and commercial real estate markets. He says New Yorkers are resilient and will come back and be "better for it."

Hosts: Carol Massar and Jason Kelly. Producer: Doni Holloway.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
